# Repo-root Docker build context hygiene.
#
# Some services share the buf-generated Go module via a relative replace
# (e.g. services/market-district/go.mod: replace qtown/proto => ../../gen/go),
# so their images MUST build with the repo root as context. This file keeps that
# context small by dropping everything a build never needs.
.git
.github
v1
engine

# Node / Nuxt
**/node_modules
**/.nuxt
**/.output
dashboard/.data

# Python
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.venv
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache

# Rust / build artifacts
**/target
**/dist
**/*.log

# Local env / secrets — never bake into an image
**/.env
**/.env.*
